data.description: NOW AVAILABLE 3 bed 2 bed home on large corner lot in popular Villages at Bocage!  Home features 2 car garage, split and open floor plan, NO CARPET, modern finishes, luxurious kitchen with stainless appliances, GAS RANGE and granite counters.  Enjoy the high ceilings and spacious feel and computer nook off large primary that includes dual vanities separate tub/shower and LARGE walk in closet!  Back patio is great for entertaining with large fenced yard and EXTENDED COVERED back patio and storage shed.  Home has it all!
